messages.title: Standing Up for Real Change
messages.content: Dear Voter, I have spoken to so many Vauxhall residents and what I hear always is that Vauxhall could be better. As a former Labour Party member, I know they are right. In fact, the improvement of the wellbeing of all residents of Vauxhall is my main interest. I joined UKIP because I am very confident of UKIP’s vision for a solid and prosperous United Kingdom – FOR A BETTER VAUXHALL.

leaflet.personalStatement: I am very confident of UKIP’s vision for a solid and prosperous United Kingdom – FOR A BETTER VAUXHALL.
